OL,3,CHomeless man's handwritten note to
OL,4,Ccommunity goes viral
OL,6,FA letter penned by a homeless man and
OL,7,Fleft in a community library in a North
OL,8,FYorkshire village has gone viral
OL,9,Fonline ` after he thanked residents
OL,10,Ffor adding "a little brightness" to
OL,11,Fhis day.
OL,13,FThe man - who we are not naming - had
OL,14,Fleft the 28-word note inside the
OL,15,Frenovated phone box, which had been
OL,16,Fturned into a community library in
OL,17,FKirk Deighton.
OL,19,FThe man explained that he is "homeless
OL,20,Fand sits by the war memorial most
OL,21,Fevenings to read".
OL,26,@rD@LOUrD@`O]
