OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1778515868
OL,3,CHomeless man's handwritten note to
OL,4,Ccommunity goes viral
OL,6,F"Having these books available adds a
OL,7,Flittle brightness to my day", he wrote.
OL,9,FOver seventy thousand people have
OL,10,Fviewed, liked and commented on the
OL,11,Fsocial media post, which was made by
OL,12,Fone of the librarians.
OL,14,FOne social media user commented: "This
OL,15,Fis so lovely! What you've done here is
OL,16,Fso much more than restore a piece of
OL,17,Fhistory."
OL,19,F"That makes it so worthwhile", said
OL,20,Fanother.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/3
