OL,3,CHomeless man's handwritten note to
OL,4,Ccommunity goes viral
OL,6,FResidents have now written a card to
OL,7,Fthe man thanking him for his kind
OL,8,Fwords and offering support should it
OL,9,Fbe required.
OL,11,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,12,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,13,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,14,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,15,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,16,Fbelow...
